snippet: A resolution demanded the immediate end to all violence in Syria. European members of the Security Council had weakened references to sanctions in an attempt to prevent a veto, to no avail.
lead_paragraph: A resolution demanded the immediate end to all violence in Syria. European members of the Security Council had weakened references to sanctions in an attempt to prevent a veto, to no avail.
